The '''Consul''' was a basic design that was used as a pattern for constructing [[Lightsaber/Legends|lightsaber]] [[Lightsaber hilt/Legends|hilts]]. It is a short hilt with bronze markings around the hilt. It was in use by [[Jedi Initiate/Legends|students]] and [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Knights]] that served with the [[New Jedi Order]] as of [[14 ABY/Legends|14 ABY]].

